{"tid":1754641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"而家我地拎住好多好牌，係時候要求政府回應民意，射返個波比佢","createTime":"2019-11-25T09:23:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T14:05:11.000Z","uid":98507,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f223292d2b9ecee1a0e8a4fb5b98c0dd2c06d36d","tid":1754641,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"立即執行撤銷暴動定性以及釋放所有示威者<br />\n同埋立即答應會進行籌備獨立調查委員會以及雙普選之工作<br />\n<br />\n雙普選最重要<br />\n因為人權法要求2020有雙普選<br />\n我地要配合人權法走要求政府咁做<br />\n如果佢敢唔做美帝自然會出手<br />\n我明大家區選大勝係要開心下<br />\n所以而家最好就係射返比政府<br />\n中間呢段時間等我地做一做過渡<br />\n佢一拒絕我地就立即開波"},{"pid":"d8f68b5952cea5ea9268c7db753436c06ff0855e","tid":1754641,"uid":98507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:24:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70ab4fcd71476ca155e25cfc485b3f13e0fcce72","tid":1754641,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">依家我哋區選贏咗，外國好關注我哋！<br />\n係咪連少少嘢都唔肯做呀？</span><br />\n<br />\n最新的tweets 一定響bot <br />\n總之<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> Retweet Like Reply </span></span>就得<br />\n㩒入👉 <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=c7e921c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">/task</span></span> 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSen. Marco Rubio<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenRubioPress/status/1198773889112956928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJma%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=638fda89\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenRubioPress%2Fstatus%2F1198773889112956928&h=2dc87735\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/S